title: High speed film blowing machine set US-SJ-45

short_description: This US-SJ-45 model extruder has a production rate of up to 55 kg of polyethylene roll film per hour. This equipment with a total power of 38 kW weighs 3.5 tons. The maximum width of the produced film is 600 mm, and the overall dimensions of the equipment are 3000*2800*4200 mm. The description also includes other models of this extruder. Their parameters and prices differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-SJ-45 modeldagi ekstruder soatiga 55 kg gacha polietilen rulonli plyonka ishlab chiqarish tezligiga ega. Umumiy quvvati 38 kW ni tashkil qiluvchi bu uskuna 3.5 tonna vaznga ega. Ishlab chiqariluvchi plyonkaning maksimal kengligi 600 mm, uskunaning umumiy o'lchamlari esa 3000*2800*4200 mm dan iborat. Tavsifda bu ekstruderning boshqa modellari ham o'rin olgan. Ularning parametr va narxlari bir-biridan farqlanadi.
